# 🎯 AUTO ASSIGNMENT ENGINE

Implement:

```ts
function autoAssignFields(columns, chartType): FieldAssignment[]
```

Rules:

* Pick lowest-cardinality categorical → x or hierarchy
* Pick numeric → y or value
* Pick second categorical → legend
* Pick time → x (if line/area)
* Pick 3rd numeric → size (bubble)

